        {
            "title": "專欄 郭嘉諾│12碼改「一Take過」舉腳贊成",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"未來12碼改為「一Take過」，可免除在補射時出現的各種爭議。Reuters\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/3c832a9bac2415d0881abdf03d2c3d1a/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250214/_2025021421191123118.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">未來12碼改為「一Take過」，可免除在補射時出現的各種爭議。Reuters</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>前幾天看到網上有報道及討論，前著名球證、現職國際足協裁判部委員會主席的哥連拿提出，會考慮未來球賽法定時間內的12碼，效法互射12碼階段時一樣，採取「一Take過」制度。\n\n</p>\n<p>免除補時機會更刺激\n\n</p>\n<p>12碼「一Take過」，意思是指球員在12碼射門中眉柱彈出或被擋出後，球賽會立即暫停並以死球重開。這個目的是避免進攻或防守球員在起腳前衝入禁區，免除在12碼補射時發生的一切混亂情況。\n\n</p>\n<p>有助減少球證「睇漏眼」\n\n</p>\n<p>有統計指出，12碼入球率高達75%，這包括了皮球被撲出後的補射入球率。如果剔除了補射機會，守門員能更加專注去撲救12碼，降低12碼的入球率，增加球賽競爭性及刺激性。\n\n</p>\n<p>這個提議，筆者認為是確實可以考慮。12碼判決一向具有爭議性，而且很多時候，12碼由判罰到主射，都浪費了很多法定時間，影響球賽進程。在主射12碼時，旁證站在底線，主球證站立位置及身體方向需要同時面對主射球員、守門員，但又需要同時觀察主射一刻有沒有雙方球員衝入禁區，三項事情同時發生時，要球證單靠肉眼判斷是非常困難。\n\n</p>\n<p>當然這情況可以利用VAR協助判決，但球例修改是要考慮整體實行性，相信這個提議對於球證整體執法將會有所幫助。郭嘉諾\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2052857/即時-體育-專欄-郭嘉諾│12碼改-一Take過-舉腳贊成",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-15 07:06:14",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "專欄 未卜先芝│熱刺曼聯齊低迷 半場難分高下",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"熱刺冬窗借入的奇雲丹素適應需時。Reuters\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/3e978101f0c9fcd90c03a298095874af/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250214/_2025021422090430967.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">熱刺冬窗借入的奇雲丹素適應需時。Reuters</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>周日英超熱刺主場對陣曼聯，熱刺連續兩場盃賽敗陣，先0:4輸畀利物浦，再1:2負阿士東維拉。球隊傷兵問題日益嚴峻，嚴重影響球隊表現，而防守向來係白百合嘅短處，剛喺轉會窗借來嘅中堅奇雲丹素亦需要時間適應，進攻能力亦大不如前，即管睇吓剛借來嘅馬菲斯泰爾能否再次入波。\n\n</p>\n<p>客隊曼聯上周末足總盃反勝李斯特城2:1，但球隊把握力仍需改善，雖然前鋒約舒亞舒克斯上場有波入，但球隊整體進攻效率低，不時要靠後防球員入波。兩隊表現相當飄忽，相信今場場面較為膠着。佩芝\n\n</p>\n<p>推介：半場主客和「和」\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2052871/即時-體育-專欄-未卜先芝│熱刺曼聯齊低迷-半場難分高下",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-15 07:06:14",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "天文台｜短暫時間有陽光 日間最高氣溫約21度 隨後一兩日早晚清涼",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"黎志偉攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/18e431afa745f91cec24b8cf6845cd18/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250215/_2025021506480025290.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">黎志偉攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>影響廣東沿岸的東北季候風正逐漸緩和。同時，一道雲帶亦覆蓋該區。\n\n</p>\n<p>本港地區今日天氣預測，短暫時間有陽光。早晚有一兩陣微雨及薄霧。日間最高氣溫約21度。吹和緩東風，稍後轉吹微風。\n\n</p>\n<p>展望明日初時較為潮濕，日間天色好轉及溫暖，隨後一兩日早晚清涼，風勢頗大，日間乾燥。下週中後期短暫時間有陽光。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4081530/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"分區氣溫\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/955bd68f8d83f24c979093919c323a07/2025-02/2025-02-15_06_29_34.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        分區氣溫\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4081531/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"九天天氣預報\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f79aed88065a3802b9e23d4c0666261a/2025-02/2025-02-15_06_36_35.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        九天天氣預報\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4081532/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"今日短暫時間有陽光。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/12f06854e633e45d3f4269fc86069ca2/2025-02/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-02-15-06-28-07_004.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        今日短暫時間有陽光。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4081533/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"日間最高氣溫約21度。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4eefc8b6c39e2cfe53143b9f94537c01/2025-02/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-02-15-06-28-10_005.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        日間最高氣溫約21度。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4081534/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"隨後一兩日早晚清涼。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a6435da38c64965edb20d87f635a3686/2025-02/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-02-15-06-27-59_001.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        隨後一兩日早晚清涼。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>隨著現時影響廣東沿岸的東北季候風今日逐漸緩和及雲帶轉薄，該區日間氣溫稍為回升。預料一股季候風補充會在星期日抵達華南沿岸，下週初該區天色大致良好，風勢頗大。預料東北季候風會在下週中至後期持續影響廣東沿岸，該區早晚清涼。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
